title: Hungary: EU must formally warn Hungary over refugee crisis violations (Amnesty International Australia)
text: ( Source : Amnesty International Australia ) The Hungarian government has invested more than 1OO million euros on razor-wire fencing and border controls to keep refugees and migrants out, triple the amount it spends yearly on receiving asylum
